headline: Cognizant lifts annual revenue forecast on strong AI demand
summary: This shift has helped the firm mitigate the effects of a volatile market. With Generative AI gaining traction, clients are increasingly integrating AI into software development cycles, streamlining operations and enhancing customer support. Cognizant expects annual revenue in the range of $20.5 billion to $21.0 billion, compared to previous outlook of the midpoint of $20.30 billion and $20.80 billion.
